{{documentation subpage}}
<!---PLEASE ADD METADATA TO THE <includeonly> SECTION AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE.--->
This template is used to produce a link in a box to a [[Subject:Books by subject|subject]].

===Parameters===
: <code>'''<nowiki>{{</nowiki>Subject box|<var>Name</var>|image=<var>Image</var>|size=<var>Size</var>|left=yes|margin=<var>Margin</var>}}'''</code>

; <code><var>Name</var></code> : The name of the subject. <!-- This defaults to the current page's name - true but let's not encourage this.  If pages or sections are moved or copied stuff breaks. -->

The following additional parameters are available. They are all optional; the default values are chosen to give a good look and feel across the project.

; {{Para|image|<var>Image</var>}} : The image to use for the subject's icon. This defaults to an image that is specified in Template:Subject box/Images/SubjectName for the subject or a generic image. There is a [[Template:Subject box/Images|list of all such images]].

; {{Para|size|<var>Size</var>}} : The width of the icon, as an integer. This is in units of pixels. The default is 32. The icon is also constrained to be at most 28 pixels high.

; {{Para|left|yes}} : Float the box to the left instead of to the right.

; {{Para|margin|<var>Margin</var>}} : The margin around the box. By default, the box is surrounded by a margin of width 0.5em, but this can be customized using {{para|margin|<var>top right bottom left</var>}} (''e.g.'', {{para|margin|0.25em 0 0.25em 0.25em}}) or removed using {{para|margin|0}} (zero).

===Examples===
{| style="background:transparent;"
|- style="font-size:120%;"
! Code<hr/> !! Result<hr/>
|-
| {{tlx|Subject box|Books by subject}}
| {{Subject box|Books by subject}}
|-
| {{tlx|Subject box|Science}}
| {{Subject box|Science}}
|-
| {{tlx|Subject box|Science|Conical flask stylised.svg}}
| {{Subject box|Science|Conical flask stylised.svg}}
|-
| {{tlx|Subject box|Science|size&#61;15}}
| {{Subject box|Science|size=15}}
|-
| {{tlx|Subject box|Science|left&#61;yes}}
| {{Subject box|Science|left=yes}}
|}
