   |pl|pl|pl|  |  |pl|pl|bd|=
   |rl|nl|bl|  |  |  |  |kl|=
||
}}
=Ruy Lopez, Riga Variation, Main Line=

Note that [[/12...Qxd8|12...Qxd8]] is literally black's only legal move.

{{ChessMid}}
